    {
      "bookmarkId": "25178845_7_16137-16154",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "16137-16154",
      "markText": "记忆的敌人不是时间，而是其他记忆。",
      "totalCount": 1513,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25178845&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=16137&rangeEnd=16154",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3f332830718032dd3f3156d?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=16137&rangeEnd=16154"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25178845_3_1228-1296",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "1228-1296",
      "markText": "“时间变慢”背后的原理是：身处危机之时，我们会对时间产生“预期”判断，多数情况下我们是在“回顾”时间，所以时间的长短体现的是记忆的密度。",
      "totalCount": 1166,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25178845&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1228&rangeEnd=1296",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3f332830718032dd3f3156d?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1228&rangeEnd=1296"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25178845_7_788-886",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "788-886",
      "markText": "大脑永不停歇地改变形状，持续地重塑自身回路；而因为你的经历独一无二，所以你神经网络里广阔而复杂的连接模式也独一无二。此外，这些模式还在不断地改变你的整个生活，“你是谁”也因此在不断变化，永不休止。",
      "totalCount": 1134,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25178845&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=788&rangeEnd=886",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3f332830718032dd3f3156d?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=788&rangeEnd=886"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25178845_9_10311-10370",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "10311-10370",
      "markText": "自动化技能有一点有趣的优势：有意识地加以干预，往往会使其表现变差。习得的熟练动作，哪怕非常复杂，最好还是不要加以干涉。",
      "totalCount": 990,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25178845&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=10311&rangeEnd=10370",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3f332830718032dd3f3156d?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=10311&rangeEnd=10370"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25178845_7_15069-15125",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "15069-15125",
      "markText": "记忆并不是一段视频，不能准确地记录你人生的每一个瞬间；它是来自往昔时光的一种脆弱的大脑状态，你要回想，它才浮现。",
      "totalCount": 900,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25178845&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=15069&rangeEnd=15125",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3f332830718032dd3f3156d?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=15069&rangeEnd=15125"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25178845_8_24738-24818",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "24738-24818",
      "markText": "那么，什么是现实呢？它就像是一套只有你能看见的电视节目，而且你无法把它关掉。好消息是，它播出的恰好是你能接收到的最有趣的节目，经过编辑，非常个性化，只为你播出。",
      "totalCount": 885,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25178845&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=24738&rangeEnd=24818",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3f332830718032dd3f3156d?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=24738&rangeEnd=24818"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25178845_7_6172-6200",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "6172-6200",
      "markText": "在没有情感关爱和认知刺激的环境中，人的大脑无法正常发育。",
      "totalCount": 882,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25178845&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=6172&rangeEnd=6200",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3f332830718032dd3f3156d?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=6172&rangeEnd=6200"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25178845_7_4042-4124",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "4042-4124",
      "markText": "从某种意义上说，你成为自己的过程，就像从一块大理石中把本就存在的可能模样雕刻出来。你之所以成为你，不是因为你大脑里生长出了什么东西，而是因为原有的一些东西被删除了。",
      "totalCount": 830,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25178845&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=4042&rangeEnd=4124",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3f332830718032dd3f3156d?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=4042&rangeEnd=4124"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25178845_8_18378-18411",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "18378-18411",
      "markText": "真实的世界并不产生这些丰富的感觉；是大脑靠着自己的官能照亮了世界。",
      "totalCount": 810,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25178845&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=18378&rangeEnd=18411",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3f332830718032dd3f3156d?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=18378&rangeEnd=18411"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25178845_7_12632-12720",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "12632-12720",
      "markText": "你的出身、文化、朋友、工作、看过的每一部电影、进行的每一场谈话，这些全都在神经系统里留下了痕迹。这些不可磨灭的、微小的印象积累起来，造就了你是什么人，也限定了你能够成为什么人。",
      "totalCount": 756,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25178845&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=12632&rangeEnd=12720",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3f332830718032dd3f3156d?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=12632&rangeEnd=12720"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25178845_7_17203-17261",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "17203-17261",
      "markText": "所以，不光有可能往大脑里植入虚构的新记忆，人们还会欣然接受它，为其点缀细节，不知不觉地把幻想编织进自己的身份认同里。",
      "totalCount": 750,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25178845&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=17203&rangeEnd=17261",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3f332830718032dd3f3156d?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=17203&rangeEnd=17261"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25178845_7_20501-20577",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "20501-20577",
      "markText": "反过来，他们发现，如孤独、焦虑、抑郁、比一般人更易忧虑等消极心理因素，则跟认知快速衰退相关。积极的特质，如有责任心、生活有目标、保持忙碌，则有保护作用。",
      "totalCount": 672,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25178845&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=20501&rangeEnd=20577",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3f332830718032dd3f3156d?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=20501&rangeEnd=20577"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25178845_8_18100-18178",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "18100-18178",
      "markText": "没有哪种生物体验到了真实的客观现实；每一种生物经过进化演变，都只感知到自己能够感知的现实部分。但推测起来，每一种生物也都认为自己的现实片段就是整个客观世界。",
      "totalCount": 672,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25178845&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=18100&rangeEnd=18178",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3f332830718032dd3f3156d?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=18100&rangeEnd=18178"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25178845_8_2057-2126",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "2057-2126",
      "markText": "脑中的外部世界画面，不一定就是对外部世界的准确再现。我们对现实的感知，与外面发生的真实情况没有太多关系，而更多地是与大脑里发生的事情有关。",
      "totalCount": 658,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25178845&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=2057&rangeEnd=2126",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3f332830718032dd3f3156d?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=2057&rangeEnd=2126"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25178845_10_4780-4854",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "4780-4854",
      "markText": "大脑里的冲突持续不断，带来的结果是：我们可以自己跟自己争论、自己咒骂自己、自己哄骗自己。但到底是谁在跟谁说话呢？全都是你，只不过是你的不同部分罢了。",
      "totalCount": 656,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25178845&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=4780&rangeEnd=4854",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3f332830718032dd3f3156d?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=4780&rangeEnd=4854"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25178845_7_2483-2528",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "2483-2528",
      "markText": "动物大脑按预设程序接线的方式通常被称为“硬接线”，而人类大脑的接线方式则叫作“现场接线”。",
      "totalCount": 612,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25178845&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=2483&rangeEnd=2528",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3f332830718032dd3f3156d?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=2483&rangeEnd=2528"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25178845_11_779-829",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "779-829",
